Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:06.20,0:04:10.51,title,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(300,0)}香水和明日和教学观摩的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.60,0:04:18.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:18.30,0:04:21.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件衣服太孩子气了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:21.70,0:04:23.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这件也是 这件也是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:24.80,0:04:26.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教学观摩吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:34.50,0:04:36.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我妈妈来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:36.00,0:04:37.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今日呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:38.10,0:04:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我家爸爸会来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:43.00,0:04:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,起立
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:44.50,0:04:45.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,行礼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:46.70,0:04:48.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸还没来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.40,0:04:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 知道这个问题怎么回答的同学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:52.00,0:04:54.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我来 我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.40,0:04:54.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还没来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.90,0:04:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一起来读吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:56.90,0:05:01.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎最后这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.60,0:05:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是迟到一会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.00,0:05:05.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,每次都一样的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:02.10,0:05:03.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:06.00,0:05:09.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸你为什么不来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明明答应我会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:14.00,0:05:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:15.50,0:05:18.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别人父母就像理所当然一样来看他们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:19.00,0:05:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我好羡慕大家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.70,0:05:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,之后就非常想念天国的妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:25.50,0:05:27.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哭了整整一晚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:32.90,0:05:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让明日也有这样的痛苦经历
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:37.40,0:05:39.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我是代替妈妈去的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:39.90,0:05:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一定要弄得象样点才行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:43.80,0:05:45.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但尽管这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.20,0:05:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我根本就没什么象样衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.40,0:05:59.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:01.40,0:06:03.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你在干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.10,0:06:05.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不起 吵醒你了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.00,0:06:07.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拿出了这么多衣服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:07.60,0:06:09.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你到底在干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.20,0:06:12.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日的教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:16.50,0:06:19.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,以前明日一直都没告诉我 我都没能去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:19.70,0:06:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,今年一定要去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:23.80,0:06:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:26.90,0:06:28.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:29.30,0:06:31.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用来也行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:32.30,0:06:34.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你讨厌姐姐来吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:35.20,0:06:36.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.70,0:06:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没有放假的日子的话姐姐也要去学校上课吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.20,0:06:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:43.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:44.20,0:06:45.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不来也没事的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:45.70,0:06:47.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以不要担心我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.70,0:06:49.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,比起这个你再不早点睡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:49.30,0:06:51.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天早上送报纸就要很累了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:52.30,0:06:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对吧？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.90,0:06:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:58.60,0:07:02.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然明日说姐姐也要上学
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.30,0:07:06.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可别的孩子的爸爸妈妈都要来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:07.10,0:07:12.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我这个中学生姐姐去的话 可能会很难为情吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:15.70,0:07:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哪怕有一件成熟点的衣服也好啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:36.80,0:07:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这…这个是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.80,0:07:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:44.80,0:07:46.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐欢迎回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:46.80,0:07:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,在公寓门前捡到一个钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.40,0:07:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,钱包?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:50.20,0:07:51.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.40,0:07:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么…办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.20,0:07:54.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐…冷静点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.70,0:07:58.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看看里面有没有写有钱包主人名字或地址之类的东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:58.70,0:08:00.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:03.40,0:08:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.60,0:08:10.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有好多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.40,0:08:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.60,0:08:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只要有这些钱的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:15.20,0:08:18.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别说这个月的房租 饭钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.30,0:08:20.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还能买明日最喜欢吃的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:21.40,0:08:24.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐你还能买西装
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:24.70,0:08:27.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对了 有了这些钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:27.40,0:08:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就可以买成熟一点衣服 然后去参加明日的教学观摩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:36.40,0:08:37.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不行不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:38.30,0:08:40.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,丢失钱包的人一定遇到麻烦了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.40,0:08:41.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是送到警察局去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:42.00,0:08:44.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐正要去送报纸吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:44.60,0:08:45.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我去吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:46.00,0:08:46.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没问题吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:47.00,0:08:47.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:03.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的没事吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:03.30,0:09:04.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:04.90,0:09:07.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐真爱瞎操心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:07.20,0:09:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,可这里面这么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:09.60,0:09:11.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便跟陌生人走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.60,0:09:28.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你 等等
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.40,0:09:31.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你是隔壁住的那小妹妹吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.20,0:09:36.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 你是隔壁大姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:37.30,0:09:38.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个钱包
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:38.40,0:09:40.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是我丢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:40.20,0:09:41.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能还给我吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:44.70,0:09:45.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真古怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:46.50,0:09:48.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽是认识的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.50,0:09:50.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是太奇怪了 姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:51.80,0:09:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,里面有张就诊卡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:54.20,0:09:55.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,上面写着三枝兰子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:59.50,0:10:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.20,0:10:05.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能找到失主太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.40,0:10:07.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,小妹妹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:07.60,0:10:09.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,仔细看看你长得很可爱啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:10.60,0:10:12.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我买点什么当礼物谢你吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:12.30,0:10:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,来吧
