Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:40.70,0:10:42.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.40,0:10:47.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,圣代 草莓蛋糕和水果布丁拼盘 都是我一直梦想能吃到的啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了 别客气吃吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:51.80,0:10:52.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:54.10,0:10:56.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要跟着陌生人走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:01.10,0:11:04.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了 讨厌甜食吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:05.30,0:11:06.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐说过 古怪的…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:06.90,0:11:09.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,对不是太认识的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.10,0:11:11.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不要随便接受人家恩惠
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:13.50,0:11:15.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我带着墨镜
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:15.50,0:11:17.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,难怪被当成坏人了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.60,0:11:18.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:22.10,0:11:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,看起来很温柔的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:28.30,0:11:29.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.70,0:11:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐也想吃蛋糕吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.60,0:11:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喂…你这样还不吃啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.90,0:11:49.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个…您请的蛋糕我能够带回家吗？
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.90,0:11:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,想跟姐姐一人一半
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:52.40,0:11:53.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,蛋糕吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:55.70,0:11:58.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,一个人吃光好啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:58.70,0:12:01.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别跟姐姐说不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.10,0:12:05.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这个 全部一个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:10.50,0:12:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能买明日最喜欢吃的蛋糕
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.90,0:12:20.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐如果是现在的我的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:20.40,0:12:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,也会跟我一样这么做的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.90,0:12:33.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,拜托麻烦一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:37.20,0:12:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太感谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:39.00,0:12:40.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别客气
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:46.10,0:12:47.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很早以前开始就有点好奇
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.30,0:12:49.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.90,0:12:53.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你跟姐姐一起住在我隔壁吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.00,0:12:54.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:55.10,0:12:56.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那么你父母呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:57.80,0:13:01.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸住在其他地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:03.30,0:13:06.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈已经过世了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.60,0:13:12.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不好意思 问了奇怪的问题
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:12.50,0:13:14.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是有点在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:14.90,0:13:15.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,没事
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:16.20,0:13:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有姐姐就够了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:19.70,0:13:20.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:21.60,0:13:28.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,只是我有时会想 为什么我没有妈妈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.70,0:13:30.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,虽然只是偶尔想起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:44.60,0:13:46.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开动了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:48.50,0:13:49.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:49.60,0:13:50.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.20,0:13:53.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,隔壁的姐姐真是好人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.00,0:13:56.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,吃完了得去谢谢她
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.00,0:13:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:58.50,0:14:01.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日已经谢过了不用去啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,而且晚饭后还要收拾收拾
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:04.00,0:14:06.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 那就
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.60,0:14:07.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:10.90,0:14:12.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,多谢款待
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.30,0:14:16.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日也说非常好吃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:16.60,0:14:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哇 仔细一看还真是个可爱的人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:21.10,0:14:23.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,从今以后我们要好好相处哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:24.20,0:14:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:25.00,0:14:25.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,再见
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:30.30,0:14:33.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,跟上次叫嚷着说我们吵得时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.60,0:14:35.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是判若两人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.50,0:14:37.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:37.40,0:14:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我如果也能这么成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.60,0:14:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那去明日的教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.40,0:14:44.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就不会让妹妹难堪了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:45.30,0:14:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个 我有个无理的请求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:50.30,0:14:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,什么?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:51.10,0:14:54.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能不能借给我您的西装呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:54.60,0:14:55.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,西装?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.60,0:14:57.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有是有 你要用来干吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:57.70,0:15:00.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妹妹的教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:00.90,0:15:02.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为是代替妈妈去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:03.20,0:15:05.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想总得打扮得大方得体些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:06.10,0:15:07.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以拜托了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.60,0:15:12.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我有时会想 为什么我没有妈妈呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:16.20,0:15:17.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:17.50,0:15:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我当鼎力相助
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:19.50,0:15:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太…太谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:20.90,0:15:22.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快上来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是 打扰了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.20,0:15:30.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,教学观摩的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.00,0:15:33.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,还是不要太花哨的好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:34.10,0:15:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,垃圾成山
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.00,0:15:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很乱 你别在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.10,0:15:41.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,淡粉色系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:41.90,0:15:43.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 还是蓝色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:45.00,0:15:48.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,三枝小姐到底是何方神圣
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:49.60,0:15:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好 就这件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:53.60,0:15:55.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种打扮感觉如何
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:03.20,0:16:04.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:04.70,0:16:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,很适合你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.30,0:16:08.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,非常成熟
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:08.20,0:16:09.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.90,0:16:11.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真的哦 要有自信啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:18.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,接下来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,喷上香水
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.30,0:16:22.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好了大功告成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:22.50,0:16:23.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,真是太谢谢了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:24.10,0:16:26.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,衣服我会送去干洗再送还的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.60,0:16:28.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不用这么在意
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:28.50,0:16:30.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明天我再帮你弄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.60,0:16:34.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:35.10,0:16:36.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎…怎么了姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.10,0:16:39.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,找邻居大姐姐借的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:41.20,0:16:42.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,你…你还化妆了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.90,0:16:43.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:43.80,0:16:46.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这样就可以代替妈妈 去参加教学观摩了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.20,0:16:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:50.50,0:16:53.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强来参加教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.20,0:16:58.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 勉强什么的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:59.70,0:17:00.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 不好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:00.90,0:17:02.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,得快点去澡堂了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:02.70,0:17:04.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 去洗澡吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.60,0:17:19.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,别勉强来参加教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我的话不行吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.60,0:17:35.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 又变回原来的样子了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:38.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,哎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:43.90,0:17:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.80,0:17:50.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是姐姐的一贯的气味
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:51.10,0:17:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐 你不是任何人的替身
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:55.50,0:17:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐就是姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:58.40,0:17:59.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,就这样就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:01.10,0:18:02.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,像平时的姐姐一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.10,0:18:08.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,嗯 我明白了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.40,0:18:24.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不想让明日留下寂寞和伤心的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:24.50,0:18:26.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我想着怎样代替妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.50,0:18:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大方得体地去参加明日的教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:31.20,0:18:36.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实我只是不想自己难堪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:41.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,所以想着如何打扮大方得体 漂亮些
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:41.30,0:18:42.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我突然意识到了这点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:43.90,0:18:45.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,注视着明日的脸庞
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:45.50,0:18:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,似乎那其中隐忍着寂寞之情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:58.40,0:19:00.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日 你在找谁啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:00.70,0:19:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不 没什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:04.30,0:19:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,不会来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:10.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,开始上课了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:11.50,0:19:13.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,因为今天是教学观摩
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:13.90,0:19:16.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,爸爸妈妈都在看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.30,0:19:17.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家就一如平日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,啊 什么 中学生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:33.60,0:19:36.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日觉得平时的我就可以的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:37.30,0:19:39.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我不觉得有什么难为情的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:51.60,0:19:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那山田同学 请从94页开始读
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:56.00,0:19:56.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:02.70,0:20:05.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,太郎最后这样说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:07.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,大家一定和你一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:07.90,0:20:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,快乐的时候快乐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:10.50,0:20:12.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,伤心的时候伤心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:11.90,0:20:13.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我在这里一直看着你哦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.90,0:20:15.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,有时候会真的发火 大声嚷嚷起来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:16.00,0:20:21.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我总是后悔 自己没有察觉明日真正的心情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:22.80,0:20:27.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,但是 我会用我的视线看着明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.80,0:20:29.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,守护着明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:30.20,0:20:31.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,抱着这种心愿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.60,0:20:33.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,能够让明日感到安心的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:33.90,0:20:37.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我算得上完成了跟妈妈的约定吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:38.60,0:20:39.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,妈妈
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:43.00,0:20:43.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:44.00,0:20:45.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,学校怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:46.30,0:20:47.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,早退了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:49.90,0:20:50.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.50,0:20:52.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:54.10,0:20:55.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,谢谢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:58.10,0:20:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:02.90,0:21:05.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,其实真的 我很希望姐姐来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:08.80,0:21:11.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,这种事情我当然知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.70,0:21:20.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,好的 那么姐姐的教学观摩明日也去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.40,0:21:22.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,那个就有点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:23.40,0:21:24.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:57.70,0:22:58.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,明日
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:58.20,0:22:59.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,怎么办
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,房东说让我们快点走人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:01.70,0:23:02.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,姐姐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:02.50,0:23:04.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,我们该去哪里啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:04.70,0:23:06.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,贫穷姐妹物语
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:06.30,0:23:08.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,公寓和樱花和搬家的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:09.10,0:23:10.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,敬请观看
